		<div id="comment_body_64357296"><p><div class="quote"><p>Renewable energy is cleaner and cheaper than any fossil fuel (or ersatz fossil fuel).</p></div><p>This is a true statement.</p><p><div class="quote"><p>Don't waste money building fools fuel infrastructure</p></div><p>This is impractical. If money were no object, then yes, stop today. But the fact is, we don't have an infinite amount of money. Not even the government has that. We have to find a way to actually *pay* for the transition to clean energy.</p><p> <i>You direction is more important than where you are.</i> We can't magically jump from 1 to 100. But if we keep going in the right direction, we'll get there.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64357296">

</div>
